    <bpmn:task id="Task_1" name="Review Request">
      <bpmn:documentation>This task involves reviewing the incoming request.

## Key Points:
- Check for completeness
- Validate requirements
- Ensure proper authorization

You can link to other elements like [Check Inventory](#Task_2) or back to [Start Process](#StartEvent_1).</bpmn:documentation>
      <bpmn:incoming>SequenceFlow_1</bpmn:incoming>
      <bpmn:outgoing>SequenceFlow_2</bpmn:outgoing>
    </bpmn:task>
    <bpmn:task id="Task_2" name="Check Inventory">
      <bpmn:documentation>**Inventory Check Process**

This task checks current inventory levels against the request.

### Steps:
1. Query inventory system
2. Compare with request quantities
3. Flag any shortages

*Related tasks:* [Review Request](#Task_1) â†’ [Process Order](#Task_3)</bpmn:documentation>
      <bpmn:incoming>SequenceFlow_2</bpmn:incoming>
      <bpmn:outgoing>SequenceFlow_3</bpmn:outgoing>
    </bpmn:task>
    <bpmn:task id="Task_3" name="Process Order">
      <bpmn:documentation>Final processing step for the order.

**Requirements:**
- Inventory must be available
- Payment method verified
- Shipping address confirmed

Link back to [Check Inventory](#Task_2) if issues arise.</bpmn:documentation>
      <bpmn:incoming>SequenceFlow_3</bpmn:incoming>
      <bpmn:outgoing>SequenceFlow_4</bpmn:outgoing>
    </bpmn:task>
    <bpmn:endEvent id="EndEvent_1" name="Order Complete">
      <bpmn:documentation>Process completion - order has been successfully processed and is ready for fulfillment.</bpmn:documentation>
